extends layout

block content
    head
        link(rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.gstatic.com')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sacramento&display=swap' rel='stylesheet')
        link(rel='stylesheet' href='css/bootstrap.min.css')
        link(rel='styleSheet' href='css/styles.css' type='text/css')
        meta(charset='utf-8')

    body
        header
            nav
                ul
                    li
                        a(href='/') Home
                    li |
                    li
                        a(href='#') Blog
            a.register(href='/register') Register
        div
            h1.recipe-title Recipes
            #home.container
                .row
                    .col-md-4
                        .card.mb-4.box-shadow
                            img.card-img-top(src='images/rice-cake.jpg' alt='Korean Rice Cake')
                            .card-body
                                p.card-text
                                | Korean rice cake, also known as &ldquo;Tteokbokki&rdquo;, has become a very well known korean street food that people must have to try when they visit South Korea. The flavor is sweet and spicy. 
                                .d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center
                                    .btn-group
                                    button.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary.btn-center(type='button') Recipes
                    .col-md-4
                        .card.mb-4.box-shadow
                            img.card-img-top(src='images/spicy_noodle.jpg' alt='')
                            .card-body
                                p.card-text
                                | A Spicy Cambodian(khmer) beef stew is one of the well-known foods in Cambodia and Southeast Asia. This noodle soup is a must have when you visit Cambodia. It is called &quot;Kuy Teav Khor Ko&quot; in Cambodian.
                                .d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center
                                    .btn-group
                                    button.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary.btn-center(type='button') Recipes
                    .col-md-4
                        .card.mb-4.box-shadow
                            img.card-img-top(src='images/friedChicken.jpg' alt='')
                            .card-body
                                p.card-text
                                | You can find fried chicken anywhere you go but if you are home and cannot go out, then make fried chicken at home with your family sounds like a good plan, right?
                                .d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center
                                    .btn-group
                                    button.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary.btn-center(type='button') Recipes
                                    
                    a.return-home(href='/') &#11013; Return Home
    
